Anxiety is our effort to try to control the past by ruminating, or the future by thinking of all possibilities in hopes that we will be “prepared” to meet the present moment. The heart is not just an organ that beats ❤️‍🔥

Your heart is a portal to the energetic, somatic, spiritual, magnetic. It deals outside of the conscious realm and operates out of linear time. The frequency of the heart in coherence creates a field around the body that effects what we magnetize in (manifestations, people, things) and what crumbles away (people, things, experiences that are not in resonance with us). The brain, that we give so much power to, is floating in the field of the heart. For true joy and alignment, we have to create space and time to connect to intuition driven from that heart space!! 

The real magic for creating a life that feels easeful and in flow is to create congruency between the heart and the mind. You know that dissonance when you’ve said “yes” to a job or a relationship because logically it looked right, but inside doesn’t feel right? That happens when we are not in alignment, when the intention and subtle directions of the heart are unheard by the bravado of the mind. 

So how do we create congruency!! Every morning I want you to have 2-3 minutes where you sit in stillness with the intention of heart and mind congruency. Visualize consistent clear communication between the heart and the mind, and then turn up the volume of the feeling that evokes.  Imagine a gold cord that moves from the head to the heart. With each breath imagine the cord getting stronger and brighter, until the brightness is at full capacity. Then imagine that brightness projecting out of your heart space so that it covers yourself and everything around you. Simply by setting this intention you create the congruency. 💕💕
